# JS / jQuery Calculator

Provide your users with a basic pocket calculator style widget. 

# Using the Library
Copy the calculator.js and styles.css file from dist/ into your project

	$(function () {
		$(".calculator").calculator();
	});

# Viewing the Demo
Serve the root of the repository from a webserver.

	python -m SimpleHTTPServer 8080
	open 'http://localhost:8080'

# Running Tests
Open SpecRunner.html in a browse
